Rating: 4
I love this recipe! Usually sub scotch for rum or leave out alcohol altogether. In addition to using it as a sauce I also cut the recipe in half and spread it in the middle of a two-layer chocolate cake below the frosting. It will be the only b/scotch sauce recipe I use in the future.

