This sauce is fabulous. I've made it for gifts and have received rave reviews. I also kept some for my family who couldn't get enough of it.

Rating: 4
The person who submitted this recipe conveyed the ingredients in the best way possible. Not only was the preparation time short, but the actual cooking time was brief and easy. The only adjustment that I made was when I substituted the rum for one teaspoon of rum extract. In the end, the sauce was smooth and very flavorable. I would recommend this recipe to my family and friends. Also, I've already added the recipe to my recipe box.

